<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Brownson Industrial Consulting Brochure</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
      font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
    }

    body{
      background:#f4f6fb;
      color:#1c2b4a;
      padding:40px;
    }

    .brochure{
      max-width:1000px;
      margin:auto;
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:12px;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .hero{
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(12,31,63,.78), rgba(12,31,63,.78)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565008447742-97f6f38c985c?q=80");
      background-size:cover;
      background-position:center;
      color:#fff;
      padding:80px 50px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      font-size:42px;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    .hero p{
      font-size:18px;
      max-width:700px;
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    .content{
      padding:50px;
    }

    .section{
      margin-bottom:40px;
    }

    .section h2{
      font-size:28px;
      margin-bottom:15px;
      border-left:5px solid #f57c00;
      padding-left:12px;
    }

    .section p{
      font-size:17px;
      line-height:1.8;
      margin-bottom:15px;
    }

    .stats{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:20px;
      margin-top:20px;
    }

    .stat{
      background:#0c1f3f;
      color:#fff;
      padding:30px;
      border-radius:10px;
      text-align:center;
    }

    .stat h3{
      font-size:34px;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .cta{
      background:linear-gradient(to right,#0c1f3f,#345d94);
      color:#fff;
      padding:40px 50px;
      text-align:center;
    }

    .cta h2{
      margin-bottom:10px;
      font-size:30px;
    }

    .cta p{
      font-size:17px;
      margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-block;
      background:#f57c00;
      color:#fff;
      text-decoration:none;
      padding:14px 28px;
      border-radius:6px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .footer{
      text-align:center;
      padding:25px;
      font-size:14px;
      color:#777;
      background:#f8f9fc;
    }

    @media(max-width:800px){
      .stats{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .hero h1{
        font-size:32px;
      }
      .content, .hero, .cta{
        padding:30px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="brochure">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Conveyor System Recovery & Downtime Reduction</h1>
      <p>
        Brownson Industrial Consulting helps manufacturers investigate equipment failures,
        identify root causes, and restore reliability through practical maintenance solutions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="section">
        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
          A production facility experienced recurring conveyor failures that disrupted product flow,
          caused line stoppages, and created avoidable downtime. Temporary fixes were being made,
          but the root causes had not been fully addressed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>
          Brownson Industrial Consulting performed a structured equipment investigation to identify
          mechanical, operational, and maintenance-related failure points.
        </p>
        <p>
          This included:
        </p>
        <p>
          • Conveyor inspection and component evaluation<br>
          • Root cause analysis of repeated stoppages<br>
          • Corrective repair recommendations<br>
          • Maintenance strategy improvements<br>
          • Reliability-focused follow-up actions
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>The Result</h2>
        <p>
          By identifying the real issues and implementing targeted corrective action,
          the facility achieved measurable performance improvements.
        </p>

        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <h3>30%</h3>
            <p>Less Downtime</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <h3>Better</h3>
            <p>Equipment Reliability</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <h3>Stronger</h3>
            <p>Maintenance Response</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h2>Why It Matters</h2>
        <p>
          Investigating recurring equipment issues instead of only reacting to failures
          helps manufacturers reduce costly downtime, improve line performance,
          and protect production output.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Need Help Solving Equipment Issues?</h2>
      <p>
        Brownson Industrial Consulting provides maintenance consulting,
        issue investigation, and reliability support for industrial operations.
      </p>
      <a href="index.html#contact" class="btn">Request a Consultation</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 Brownson Industrial Consulting | BrownsonIndustrial.com
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
